name: Special Edition Card for chucho - The Alchemist
description:
No need to worry, Alchemist has everything you need!

When Necromancer attacks the enemy and Paladin becomes tanks, of course there are still some difficult situations that they face sometimes. That's when the Alchemist plays an important role. Alchemist brings various items that can support his two friends during the journey. Other than that, he also always brings several potions that have different functions, such as increasing blood or speed.
